        <mxCell id="step2_body" value="AskUserQuestion으로&#10;맥락 3-4문항 수집&#10;&#10;· 타깃 고객&#10;· 산출물 형식&#10;· 핵심 포인트" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FAF9F5;strokeColor=#D1CFC5;fontColor=#141413;fontFamily=Helvetica;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
